snippet.title: Paradise Killer - Official PlayStation and Xbox Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Paradise Killer is heading to PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X/S, and Xbox One on March 16, 2022. Watch the latest Paradise Killer trailer for a look at what to expect. A free update for all available versions of the detective adventure game is also coming, featuring new quests, new music, and more.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #ParadiseKiller
